title: Act2_EveMeeting_P2N9
---
/// no repeat
<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Oh, Cyrus! Didn’t think you’d be back this soon.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Has anything happened yet?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Uh...no?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: That’s good to hear. Don’t go anywhere until I’m back.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Wait, where are you going?
Eve: If this has something to do with the monsters, you need to let your dispatcher know. It’s too risky to go out on your own.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: You wouldn’t understand, you need to stay where it’s safe.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Don’t treat me like a child, at least let me come with you.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: What happens to me is unimportant, sometimes a sacrifice is necessary to save the rest.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: But you’re part of “everyone,” Cyrus, you won’t just be hurting yourself.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I’m sorry, Eve.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Hey! You-
Eve: ...And he’s fast.
===


