title: Act2_PostCombat_P2End
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: [i]No matter how much I prepare, I still can’t beat it![/i]

<<set_portrait YarnManager PoliceNPC>>
???: Hey! You the one who called in?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Who are—?

<<set_portrait YarnManager PoliceNPC>>
Guard: Prismatic Security. Good work holding it in place, Captain Luna will finish the rest.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: What a nasty looking thing.

Luna begins fighting the monster. (TODO sfx??)

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: She can handle it all on her own?

<<set_portrait YarnManager PoliceNPC>>
Guard: You must not know Luna.

<<set_portrait YarnManager PoliceNPC>>
Guard: Pretty smart for a false human to mimic the mayor, they’d never be near a memory monster. No wonder we never caught him.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: What do you mean?

<<set_portrait YarnManager PoliceNPC>>
Guard: Memory monsters won’t attack their own kind. The only real way to tell if someone’s a false human is to put them in a monster’s path. 

<<set_portrait YarnManager FalseHumanBoss>>
Memory Monster: RRRRAAAAA-
<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: Alright, I’ve had my fun.

Stab SFX (TODO)

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: Start the cleanup.

<<set_portrait YarnManager PoliceNPC>>
Guard: Yes, captain!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: You.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Me?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: Heh.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Do I know you?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: You could say that.

Stab SFX (TODO)

<<set_portrait YarnManager PoliceNPC>>
Guard: What are you doing!!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: He’s the other false human. I knew who he’s trying to mimic.

The Assimilation begins (TODO show this somehow)

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: [i]No.[/i]

<<set_portrait YarnManager PoliceNPC>>
Guard: The Assimilation! The other false human is still out there!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: Cyrus, is it really you??

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Not...again...
===